APPLICATION : MovRecorder 1.3 Incl Keygen

       TYPE : Video Recorder
        WWW : http://www.movrecorder.com
    RELDATE : no idea
 PROTECTION : Aspack / Serial
 CRKRELDATE : 09/04/2008

INSTALLATION: Install.
              Use keygen to generate your "Site License" serial.

       NOTES: 
              The name function in the keygen has the only purpose
              to make your serial unique to you. You can still register
              MovRecorder with any name with the generated key.
              Please use chars like a-z and/or numbers. Chars like %_# )]/!
              will work but might be banned in future versions.
              
              Nuff said. Enjoy! / ONY

       ABOUT:
       
              Mov Recorder is the easiest way to record QuickTime streaming Video
              or Audio content. With one click, you can save music videos, music,
              radio broadcasts, subscription or pay-per-view content, corporate
              webcasts, and anything else! Save your recordings as files on your
              PC, and watch them anytime you like, even without an Internet
              connection. It support all major protocols.
              
              Main Features:

              * Record quicktime streaming(mov, mp4) to your pc.
              * Multi-URLs are recorded simultaneously.
